<p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff"><strong><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">一、公司介绍</span></strong></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">阿斯利康是一家以创新为驱动的全球综合型生物制药企业，不但拥有一支业内领先的庞大研发团队，更注重合作，先后有数位诺贝尔奖获得者曾和阿斯利康一起为创新药物产品的研发贡献力量。阿斯利康致力于研制、开发、生产和营销卓有成效的处方药品，并提供专业的医疗服务，在消化、心血管、中枢神经、呼吸、肿瘤、麻醉和抗感染等领域处于领先地位，名列《财富》杂志全球500强。</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">作为中国处方药市场领先的跨国制药公司，阿斯利康现有10,000多名员工，分布在生产、销售、临床研究和新产品开发等领域，业务遍及中国主要城市，包括香港地区。</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif"></span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">在阿斯利康，我们以推动更广阔的科学领域为目标，以消除人类的疾病并降低因疾病引起的死亡为主要职责。2017阿斯利康校园招聘火热启动中，请加入我们！</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff"><br></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff"><strong><br><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">二、试翼计划</span></strong></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">阿斯利康2017试翼计划，将为有志成为医学代表的优秀应届毕业生提供学习和实践的机会，让他们为即将开始的职业生涯累积可贵经验，掌握实用技能，助他们在未来的广阔职场蓝天，展翼高飞。实习期间表现优异者将正式受聘为阿斯利康员工，开启无限辉煌的事业蓝图。</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><br></span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff"><strong><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">三、招聘岗位</span></strong></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">Medical Representative-医学代表培训生</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">公司名称：</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;times new roman&quot;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">AstraZeneca Global Commercial Organization &nbsp; </span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">阿斯利康 GCO中国</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; BACKGROUND: white; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px"><span style="TEXT-DECORATION: underline"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">职责</span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">：</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; BACKGROUND: white; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">- 熟练掌握产品知识、销售技巧等各项技能</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; BACKGROUND: white; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">- 遵循国家，行业和公司的法规，秉持高标准的商业规范，在导师指导下,在区域内协助推广公司的产品，实现销售增长</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; BACKGROUND: white; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">- 配合销售及市场部，协助组织各类学术会议</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; BACKGROUND: white; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">- 协助建立业务所需的一系列档案</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; BACKGROUND: white; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">- 具备较强的学习能力和适应性，以公司批准的用途、用法为准则，准确地向工作对象提供药物的特点、疗效及注意事项等资料，并告知医生有关的禁忌症、副作用及预防措施</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; BACKGROUND: white; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px"><span style="TEXT-DECORATION: underline"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">要求</span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">：</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; BACKGROUND: white; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">- 本科及以上学历，医学、药学等生命科学相关专业</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; BACKGROUND: white; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">- 在校期间，具有与销售相关的社会实践经验</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; BACKGROUND: white; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">- 热情自信，积极进取</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; BACKGROUND: white; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">- 具有吃苦耐劳精神，能承受较大的工作压力</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; BACKGROUND: white; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">- 具备较强的学习能力和适应性</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; BACKGROUND: white; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif">- 良好的沟通能力和人际交往能力</span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; BACKGROUND: white; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif"></span>&nbsp;</p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FONT-FAMILY: verdana; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, sans-serif"></span></p><p style="FONT-SIZE: 12px; FO